    <string name="privacy_policy_content">Terms of Service\n\n1. Introduction\nWelcome to RWAQ Coffee. By using our application, you agree to these terms.\n\n2. Services &amp; Accounts\n• Eligibility: You must be at least 18 years old to use our services.\n• Account: You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account information.\n\n3. Orders &amp; Payments\n• Payment: We accept various payment methods including credit cards and digital wallets.\n• Pricing: All prices are subject to change without prior notice.\n• Refunds: Refund requests are processed on a case-by-case basis.\n\n4. Delivery\nWe provide delivery to specific areas mentioned in the app. Delivery times are estimates and not guaranteed.\n\n5. Intellectual Property\nAll content, logos, and graphics on this app are the property of RWAQ Coffee.\n\n----------------\n\nPrivacy Policy\n\n1. Information We Collect\nWe collect personal information necessary to process your orders, such as your name, phone number, email, and delivery address.\n\n2. How We Use Your Data\n• To process and deliver your orders.\n• To improve our app functionality.\n• To send promotional offers (only with your consent).\n\n3. Data Sharing\nWe do not sell your personal data. We only share necessary details with third parties essential for service delivery.</string>
